{"tid":813828,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大亞灣藏化學品倉庫　委員指頂得住10級颱風","createTime":"2018-09-10T17:47:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-10T23:17:04.000Z","uid":5195,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"745c32466f711ac59018769bbd25abecc4f45bd8","tid":813828,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T17:47:14.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=jwgvwYm1PccCAHRL%2FKo1PwEk2Noh57F05xbgvjQdsX8%3D&h=28210e0d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】廣東大亞灣核電站安全諮詢委員會今日在深圳大亞灣召開會議，委員會主席何鍾泰在會後指，一般核電廠有40年壽命，而大亞灣核電廠今年已成立21年，該核電廠需於17至18年後再向國家安全局申請延續或退疫，他認為大亞灣很大機會延續運作。<br />\n<br />\n何鍾泰在會上透露，大亞灣核電廠及嶺澳核電廠於今年上半年，並無發生任何國際核事故分級標準0級或以上運行事件，但鑑於日本及天津曾發生核事故及爆炸，該核電廠在6月及8月亦有進行化學品應急處理綜合演習。<br />\n<br />\n不過，委員曹王敏賢承認，大亞灣核電廠有小型化學品倉庫，倉庫內主要存放清潔劑及漂白水，強調沒有存放劇毒化學品，對大亞灣核電廠的安全有信心，更指「10級颱風、7級地震都頂得順」，直言若有事故不能說對本港沒影響，但相信影響不大。<br />\n<br />\n資料顯示，在今年上半年，大亞灣核電廠及嶺澳核電廠一、二期年度累計上網電量達208.81億度；由1994至今，大亞灣已供2,052億度電輸港，佔本港電量四分一。"},{"pid":"6b37e84317655b624045f9ff64ff9a38d7752406","tid":813828,"uid":2419,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T17:51:46.000Z","msg":"沒事兒 沒事兒"},{"pid":"d665fac2c1d3112e0aa3f775fa66d9908e8c3bba","tid":813828,"uid":4525,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T18:08:26.000Z","msg":"出多咪死35人"},{"pid":"3dd0d351fde65521fa2d8550d0bd11873dee1cf8","tid":813828,"uid":51294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T18:10:58.000Z","msg":"諗起天津港"},{"pid":"e6ee9b593780c824758bd2ef9619feed0c800f13","tid":813828,"uid":24140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T18:16:31.000Z","msg":"颶風好似係12級風<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69c46b4707dda42fa45013698d9eb20a6e1827f6","tid":813828,"uid":65984,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T18:22:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/11/022159_24af6659c1cd2d45fd54556cf5531133.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F11%2F022159_24af6659c1cd2d45fd54556cf5531133.jpg&h=b52a9e00&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fe8451f095781f696485641f8384b266626635c6","tid":813828,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T23:15:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/11/071532_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F11%2F071532_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=74c47a40&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f6f635f5e1aad2c4e8a9785e8b3827ca0fa09171","tid":813828,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T23:17:04.000Z","msg":"就算真係出事 都唔會通報㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}